name: Rochelle Pangilinan
description: '''Rochelle Pangilinan-Solinap''' (born May 23, 1982) is a Filipino actress, dancer and singer. She began her career as one of the original members of the [[SexBomb Girls]], who gained prominence through the variety show ''[[Eat Bulaga!]]''. She later appeared in television programs, most notably in ''[[Daisy Siete]]'', and portrayed Agane in the 2016 fantasy drama series ''[[Encantadia (2016 TV series)|Encantadia]]''. In 2007, she briefly rebranded as a rap artist under the name '''RoC'''.
